{"type": "article", "id": 20691, "title": "护肤品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-14T07:30:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607153613kP2CUsWBIaEGFuxo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套护肤品，看起来像是果酱瓶。Nubia 宣称是用纯自然材料提取并通过手工制作的，适合 20 岁以上的女性，这套包装也显得很可爱。瓶子是半透明的，可以看到里面带有一点颜色的液体，有点朦胧。瓶盖上画出了天然成分的图案，瓶身上的文字也故意写出了手工感，都是女生所喜欢的元素。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150540wovMaLysESm2AJ9j.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"462\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85873606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150541kYDTiHEwBVZ4Fy5J.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71189591\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150541KYZi6uRg5o7bHyk9.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"414\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76951673\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150542PUQsnuKpV5L8NDHw.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"494\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.91821561\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150542seVhDQdEuAUHGb30.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"413\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76765799\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}